                            <comment id="12995627" author="eclark" created="Thu, 17 Feb 2011 01:23:42 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I was thinking of something more simple than that.  basically I want a rest interface to HTable.get(List&amp;lt;Get&amp;gt; gets).&lt;br/&gt;
Wouldn&apos;t a Regex would require a scan over all row keys.  Something that would be much slower than a multiget.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
