                            <comment id="13009453" author="eclark" created="Mon, 21 Mar 2011 22:33:49 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;So the url would be /table/multiget?row=rk1&amp;amp;row=rk2&amp;amp;row=rk3&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
